Class Ride

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ride
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Ride>

    public class Ride
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Ride>
    Model the rides. A ride holds the starting and finishing coordinates of the ride, the earliest start step, and the latest finish step.
